            "answer_text": "1) Google Python Class => Old but Gold Watch entire series. Do execute the code as you watch the video. Pause the video , execute as he says then only move ahead.  2) Python Tutorial: Learn Python For Free | Codecademy Start this course and do not take more than 7 days 3) Solve problems here: CodingBat Python Whenever you get bored , try to explore about these things. Just see one basic video(Search on Youtube and watch the most viewed video on that topic) explaining what is it and what it does - Pandas - Jupyter Notebook - Django/Flask - Git/Github - How to install packages in Python ? What is PIP in python ? - How to use third-party APIs in Python ? - How Machine Learning works ? - Try to find and generate QR Code using Python for any message you want. Trying out above things will show the power of Python libraries available for free out in the open and also increase your curiosity level to solve a problem just by programming. ",
